  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">21ST CENTURY SKILLS TRAINING 4 KIDS IN NIGERIA</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We plan to train 100  public school children using 21st century skills such as Critical thinking, Creativity, Communication, and Collaboration to cope with present day challenges beyond the classroom. Digital Literacy, Financial Literacy, Media Literacy, Health literacy, Global awareness, Life skills, Citizenship &amp; Resilience will be taught. The training will take place in a 5 days summer camp in Kwara State. Also children will be provided with materials such as  Chess, Cashflow , Monopoly etc.</narrative>
  </description>
